            <title>[SOLR-13805] Solr - generates an NPE when calling /solr/admin/health on standalone solr</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-13805</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;steps to reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;

