&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then nav to: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/admin/health&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/admin/health&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

